{"tid":165584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子承認強暴12歲女童 當庭釋放原因是女童看起來像是16歲","createTime":"2017-03-21T12:54:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-22T01:02:02.000Z","uid":22675,"like":13,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1cbd6826ff9b2fa8917655860f1742c0cf9bf2a0","tid":165584,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T12:54:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpwYCGCK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpwYCGCK.jpg&h=79651242&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">切希拉克（Daniel Cieslak）獲判無罪。（圖取自都會報）</span><br />\n2017-03-21  07:21<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕蘇格蘭一名男子坦承自己性侵12歲女童，結果格拉斯哥高等法院法官判他無罪當庭釋放，原因是女童看起來像是16歲。<br />\n《都會報》報導，現年21歲的切希拉克（Daniel Cieslak），2年前在愛丁堡計程車站遇到12歲的被害人與其13歲朋友，他以為2人分別是16歲與17歲，把她們帶去派對玩樂，之後與被害人發生性行為。<br />\n報導指出，格拉斯哥高等法院法官史考特（Elizabeth Scott）表示，切希拉克是從2人於計程車的對話判斷其年紀，且發生關係後被害人隔天早上才離開，並無苦惱與痛苦。史考特認為，嚴格意義下，與12歲女童做愛是犯法的，但此案為特殊狀況。<br />\n報導表示，法官史考特指出，切希拉克一直以為對方已達法定年齡，沒有操縱或欺騙被害人，且所有證人都認為女童看起來像是16歲，因此判切希拉克無罪。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2010952\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2010952&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9AhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=bb87cc19\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2010952&h=03c224cc\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2010952</a>"},{"pid":"2959aee7ecddc136e2276d146129f5f075b03b70","tid":165584,"uid":5858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T13:00:06.000Z","msg":"咁識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d49905ee06b16b4811d3b1081e2293e1eaebaa30","tid":165584,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T13:07:22.000Z","msg":"其實應該係十二歲女童要識防護自己，唔關男主事，唔通過過想屌前都問佢拎身份證<img src=\"/a